no multithread and no cache system in the former version
don't have more lines or columns in a line equal or greater than 2 ^ 32
Core -> utilities (CLI commands, filesystem interop, project configuration, etc... this must be in the former version) & 
        miscellaneous validations (CLI commands validation, project integration, etc... don't need to be in the former version)
Tear (.tear) -> cache (don't need to be in the former version)
Brain (.brain) -> global configuration not affecting the cache (don't need to be in the former version)
Sclera (.sclera) -> global configuration affecting the cache (don't need to be in the former version)
Cornea (.cornea) -> project configuration file, for the compilation units
Retina (.retina) -> Iris native library format (don't need to be in the former version)
Pupil (.pupil) -> code for the GPU (or TPU or others...) to execute, where we do the lex and parse, and output the ast (don't need to be in the former version)
Iris (.iris) -> code for the CPU to execute, where we do the lex and parse, and output the ast
Lens -> static analyzer, where we validate the ast, evaluate compile-time code, mutate the ast if needed (if static reflection gets these capabilities), and output the IR
Optic -> optimizer over the IR
Cilliary -> lsp server (don't need to be in the former version)
Choroid -> debugger
Nerve -> linker
Macula -> bundle generator (don't need to be in the former version), documentation generator and test executor